Analysts await Travelport Worldwide Ltd (NYSE:TVPT) to report earnings on August, 3 before the open. They expect $0.14 EPS, down 39.13% or $0.09 from last year’s $0.23 per share. TVPT’s profit will be $17.41 million for 25.70 P/E if the $0.14 EPS becomes a reality. After $0.45 actual EPS reported by Travelport Worldwide Ltd for the previous quarter, Wall Street now forecasts -68.89% negative EPS growth. 


